1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,980
=Episode 15=

16
00:01:46,460 --> 00:01:47,460
Hello, Miss Rao.

17
00:01:47,620 --> 00:01:48,620
We finally meet.

18
00:01:49,130 --> 00:01:50,900
I am an actuary
of the Beauty Pearl Society.

19
00:01:51,290 --> 00:01:53,690
The instructions I received
are to cooperate with you fully.

20
00:01:55,260 --> 00:01:56,050
Go ahead.

21
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:57,490
what else do you need me to do?

22
00:02:00,900 --> 00:02:01,850
I need to gain access

23
00:02:01,850 --> 00:02:03,540
to an offshore account.

24
00:02:23,780 --> 00:02:25,900
(Username and Password)

25
00:02:25,900 --> 00:02:30,020
(SECURE CONNECTION)

26
00:02:31,100 --> 00:02:32,780
(Evil acts are carried out
with impunity,)

27
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:35,370
(vainly trying to cover
the sky with one hand.)

28
00:02:36,730 --> 00:02:37,690
(But I know)

29
00:02:38,890 --> 00:02:39,980
(the destination I want)

30
00:02:40,610 --> 00:02:41,780
(is right before my eyes.)

31
00:02:43,540 --> 00:02:44,340
(Bai Muran,)

32
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:48,220
(do you still remember the knife
that pushed me into the abyss?)

33
00:02:51,540 --> 00:02:53,940
(Linwei Alley - Lane 21)

34
00:02:59,850 --> 00:03:00,660
Bai Xia.

35
00:03:01,410 --> 00:03:02,220
Bai Xia!

36
00:03:27,610 --> 00:03:28,940
Hey, Rao Yuci.

37
00:03:29,730 --> 00:03:30,340
Don't forget,

38
00:03:30,340 --> 00:03:31,380
you have a weakness too.

39
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:33,660
You dragged Bai Xia into this
to make me suffer.

40
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:35,250
Don't think you'll have it easy either.

41
00:03:35,260 --> 00:03:36,940
I won't let your parents off the hook.

42
00:03:44,260 --> 00:03:47,700
(Rao Shusheng,
Examination Item: Brain MRI Plain Scan)

43
00:03:57,980 --> 00:03:58,780
Hello?

44
00:03:59,380 --> 00:04:00,130
Zhang.

45
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:02,820
Rao Shusheng, if you don't pay
back the money,

46
00:04:03,060 --> 00:04:04,600
I'm going to corner you at your house.

47
00:04:05,540 --> 00:04:06,380
Say something!

48
00:04:14,660 --> 00:04:16,100
Hippocampal cerebral infarction.

49
00:04:16,810 --> 00:04:17,780
The doctor said

50
00:04:18,490 --> 00:04:20,050
I can't take any more shocks.

51
00:04:21,050 --> 00:04:21,850
Liangliang,

52
00:04:21,850 --> 00:04:22,620
(Rao Shusheng)

53
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:23,780
it was you who told me

54
00:04:23,780 --> 00:04:25,460
to buy those houses in Linwei Alley.

55
00:04:25,780 --> 00:04:26,540
You have

56
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:28,170
to help me settle the money I owe.

57
00:04:28,580 --> 00:04:29,220
Otherwise,

58
00:04:29,220 --> 00:04:30,980
I'm a dead man.

59
00:04:32,460 --> 00:04:33,460
Don't you know

60
00:04:33,460 --> 00:04:34,900
what has happened, Mr. Rao?

61
00:04:37,290 --> 00:04:38,100
I know.

62
00:04:38,460 --> 00:04:39,220
I know.

63
00:04:39,220 --> 00:04:40,220
Between you and Yuci,

64
00:04:40,220 --> 00:04:41,580
there might be a misunderstanding.

65
00:04:42,050 --> 00:04:43,220
There is no misunderstanding

66
00:04:43,220 --> 00:04:44,340
between Rao Yuci and me.

67
00:04:44,810 --> 00:04:46,580
Do you want to hear our story?

68
00:04:47,170 --> 00:04:47,980
No need.

69
00:04:48,930 --> 00:04:50,250
I just want you to help me.

70
00:04:51,460 --> 00:04:53,100
I'm truly at the end of my rope.

71
00:04:53,370 --> 00:04:54,370
You really don't care

72
00:04:54,370 --> 00:04:55,850
about your daughter at all.

73
00:04:57,490 --> 00:04:59,580
That Rao Yuci and I
have come to this point,

74
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:01,980
you've been a huge help, Mr. Rao.

75
00:05:03,250 --> 00:05:05,290
You've always thought she was a monster.

76
00:05:05,660 --> 00:05:07,170
But have you ever considered

77
00:05:07,980 --> 00:05:09,220
that the biggest monster

78
00:05:10,050 --> 00:05:10,850
is you?

79
00:05:11,610 --> 00:05:13,220
You failed in your futures investment.

80
00:05:13,930 --> 00:05:15,140
I used Chuxia's clients

81
00:05:15,140 --> 00:05:16,460
and funds to help you

82
00:05:17,020 --> 00:05:17,980
just to drive a wedge

83
00:05:17,980 --> 00:05:20,100
between you and Rao Yuci.

84
00:05:21,140 --> 00:05:22,780
You thought she was a lunatic

85
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:24,810
and agreed to let her
enter the treatment center.

86
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:26,370
But you didn't know

87
00:05:27,460 --> 00:05:29,250
that the knife she used to stab Mrs. Rao

88
00:05:29,660 --> 00:05:32,540
was placed under the printer
in advance by Bai Muran on my orders.

89
00:05:32,540 --> 00:05:33,220
Zhaohe,

90
00:05:34,050 --> 00:05:35,020
I was wrong.

91
00:05:38,410 --> 00:05:40,170
Your failed investment in Linwei Alley

92
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,950
was because
I sought you out intentionally.

93
00:05:42,250 --> 00:05:43,050
The purpose

94
00:05:43,100 --> 00:05:44,220
was to aggravate the conflict

95
00:05:44,220 --> 00:05:45,660
between you and your daughter

96
00:05:45,660 --> 00:05:47,370
to make the resentment run deeper.

97
00:05:47,540 --> 00:05:48,340
Zhaohe,

98
00:05:49,140 --> 00:05:50,220
I regret it.

99
00:05:51,780 --> 00:05:54,140
I've failed our daughter.

100
00:05:54,730 --> 00:05:55,810
I've failed Yuci!

101
00:05:55,810 --> 00:05:57,780
Did you really think
I was helping you make money?

102
00:05:58,300 --> 00:06:00,140
- You were just the first step
- I was wrong.

103
00:06:00,140 --> 00:06:01,520
in my plan to strike at Rao Yuci.

104
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,460
I was wrong.

105
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:04,730
Now, your daughter hates you to death.

106
00:06:06,490 --> 00:06:07,980
She won't save you.

107
00:06:08,850 --> 00:06:10,410
And I won't save you either.

108
00:06:10,610 --> 00:06:12,410
No one will save you.

109
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,660
Look, what happened to him?

110
00:06:29,660 --> 00:06:30,290
Someone fell over there!

111
00:06:30,290 --> 00:06:31,220
Call an ambulance, quick!

112
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:33,340
(Waiting Area)

113
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:42,980
(Emergency Room)

114
00:07:03,340 --> 00:07:04,290
The doctor said

115
00:07:05,660 --> 00:07:07,810
he had a hippocampal
cerebral infarction.

116
00:07:09,370 --> 00:07:10,980
The chances of him

117
00:07:12,170 --> 00:07:13,810
waking up are unknown.

118
00:07:30,140 --> 00:07:30,930
How is he?

119
00:07:33,490 --> 00:07:34,700
Out of danger.

120
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:38,780
But we don't know
when he will regain consciousness.

121
00:07:43,900 --> 00:07:45,410
The score I'm going to settle

122
00:07:47,140 --> 00:07:48,780
might end up hurting me too.

123
00:07:50,850 --> 00:07:52,290
If anything happens to me,

124
00:07:53,250 --> 00:07:54,140
I can't let my mother

125
00:07:54,140 --> 00:07:55,580
face all this alone.

126
00:07:57,020 --> 00:08:05,140
(Stocks: Sell All)

127
00:08:05,140 --> 00:08:06,250
(Baiying Business Investigation)

128
00:08:06,250 --> 00:08:07,540
I called you all here today

129
00:08:07,540 --> 00:08:09,050
to calculate exactly how much

130
00:08:09,410 --> 00:08:10,810
Rao Shusheng owes.

131
00:08:10,820 --> 00:08:11,850
How much do I need to pay back?

132
00:08:11,850 --> 00:08:13,100
The loan agreement we have

133
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:14,100
states it very clearly.

134
00:08:14,460 --> 00:08:15,610
Here, give it to me.

135
00:08:15,610 --> 00:08:16,290
Give me the IOU first.

136
00:08:16,290 --> 00:08:17,100
It's been six months.

137
00:08:17,170 --> 00:08:18,250
The interest has piled up.

138
00:08:18,250 --> 00:08:20,290
If you don't pay now,
we will take legal action.

139
00:08:20,580 --> 00:08:21,900
Please rest assured.

140
00:08:22,580 --> 00:08:24,850
Once Miss Rao and I
have verified everything,

141
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:26,780
the payments will be transferred

142
00:08:26,780 --> 00:08:28,700
successively into each of your accounts.

143
00:08:30,850 --> 00:08:31,660
(Paying the debt)

144
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:33,940
(is not for Rao Shusheng)

145
00:08:35,130 --> 00:08:36,490
(but for my mother.)

146
00:08:40,940 --> 00:08:42,420
Was my acting okay?

147
00:08:42,980 --> 00:08:44,340
You played the part very well.

148
00:08:44,610 --> 00:08:46,420
It was completely
beyond my expectations.

149
00:08:46,890 --> 00:08:47,770
Thank you.

150
00:08:49,580 --> 00:08:50,490
Ms. Bai Xia,

151
00:08:52,100 --> 00:08:53,180
I've leased this house

152
00:08:53,460 --> 00:08:54,700
for three years.

153
00:08:55,460 --> 00:08:56,250
You and Mr. Xu

154
00:08:56,250 --> 00:08:57,610
can live here with peace of mind.

155
00:08:58,100 --> 00:08:59,980
Don't worry about the rent or anything.

156
00:09:00,980 --> 00:09:01,770
No, no.

157
00:09:01,940 --> 00:09:02,820
That won't do.

158
00:09:03,300 --> 00:09:05,010
How can we take advantage
of you like this?

159
00:09:05,010 --> 00:09:06,250
This is what I owe you.

160
00:09:07,130 --> 00:09:08,420
You owe me?

161
00:09:09,650 --> 00:09:11,100
You've been helping me all along.

162
00:09:11,610 --> 00:09:13,220
How can you owe me?

163
00:09:18,010 --> 00:09:19,010
Ms. Bai Xia,

164
00:09:20,460 --> 00:09:22,130
there are some things

165
00:09:23,530 --> 00:09:25,220
I can't tell you right now.

166
00:09:26,700 --> 00:09:27,530
Soon,

167
00:09:28,130 --> 00:09:29,890
I'll be away for a while.

168
00:09:30,650 --> 00:09:31,340
You and Mr. Xu

169
00:09:31,340 --> 00:09:32,610
just live here comfortably.

170
00:09:35,890 --> 00:09:36,700
Yuci...

171
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:44,490
While you're out there,

172
00:09:46,530 --> 00:09:47,890
remember to eat on time.

173
00:09:52,010 --> 00:09:53,610
Thank you, Ms. Bai Xia.

174
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:09,060
Does your situation

175
00:10:12,130 --> 00:10:13,940
have something to do with Liangliang?

176
00:10:19,530 --> 00:10:20,770
Finally, we meet, Ms. Bai.

177
00:10:21,100 --> 00:10:22,880
I am an actuary
of the Beauty Pearl Society.

178
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:27,520
There are so many rumors
about the Beauty Pearl Society now.

179
00:10:27,940 --> 00:10:29,820
How do I know you're not a fraud?

180
00:10:44,650 --> 00:10:45,580
As proof,

181
00:10:45,980 --> 00:10:47,970
not only do we know
what's on your mind, Ms. Bai,

182
00:10:48,180 --> 00:10:49,890
but we also know the answers you want.

183
00:10:52,530 --> 00:10:53,340
In fact,

184
00:10:53,650 --> 00:10:54,850
we also know everything

185
00:10:54,850 --> 00:10:56,420
between you and Rao Yuci.

186
00:11:01,370 --> 00:11:02,530
The Beauty Pearl Society

187
00:11:02,610 --> 00:11:04,220
wants to make a deal with you.

188
00:11:06,820 --> 00:11:07,530
Place the bug

189
00:11:07,530 --> 00:11:09,130
in Jiang Dongchao's office.

190
00:11:09,180 --> 00:11:11,060
You want me to betray Mr. Jiang?

191
00:11:11,820 --> 00:11:13,010
Betraying Jiang Dongchao

192
00:11:13,010 --> 00:11:14,300
is something you've done before,

193
00:11:15,100 --> 00:11:16,250
only you didn't succeed.

194
00:11:18,060 --> 00:11:18,850
Isn't that right?

195
00:11:23,820 --> 00:11:24,850
Finish this task,

196
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:27,690
and the Beauty Pearl Society will help you
find the person in the photo.

197
00:11:40,490 --> 00:11:41,530
Rest assured, Ms. Bai.

198
00:11:42,370 --> 00:11:43,850
If this is successful,

199
00:11:44,060 --> 00:11:46,370
it will certainly help improve
your status in Lysen.

200
00:11:53,340 --> 00:11:54,460
You don't trust me?

201
00:11:54,650 --> 00:11:55,460
Bai Liangliang,

202
00:11:56,890 --> 00:11:58,300
your good friend Rao Yuci

203
00:12:00,530 --> 00:12:01,580
is smarter than you.

204
00:12:03,700 --> 00:12:05,060
Bai Liangliang...

205
00:12:06,010 --> 00:12:07,770
You're so much like I was
when I was young.

206
00:12:10,100 --> 00:12:11,100
Your ambition is showing.

207
00:12:12,250 --> 00:12:14,010
Especially you, Bai Liangliang.

208
00:12:15,650 --> 00:12:18,300
Why do you always want
to be the one waiting to swoop in?

209
00:12:26,130 --> 00:12:27,730
Hello, Miss Gao.

210
00:12:38,220 --> 00:12:39,220
The acquisition plan

211
00:12:39,220 --> 00:12:41,360
for those green building
materials companies has been concluded.

212
00:12:41,770 --> 00:12:43,220
Mr. Jiang, you don't need to worry.

213
00:12:46,580 --> 00:12:47,420
What do you mean?

214
00:12:48,250 --> 00:12:49,060
I want to resign.

215
00:12:50,300 --> 00:12:51,340
I think what you need

216
00:12:51,340 --> 00:12:52,220
isn't me,

217
00:12:52,650 --> 00:12:53,530
but a bargaining chip

218
00:12:53,770 --> 00:12:54,980
to break free from Baiye,

219
00:12:55,250 --> 00:12:56,460
steady Mr. Li,

220
00:12:56,610 --> 00:12:57,340
and continue

221
00:12:57,340 --> 00:12:58,730
to control Lysen.

222
00:12:58,730 --> 00:12:59,420
Yes.

223
00:13:01,700 --> 00:13:03,220
You are my greatest bargaining chip.

224
00:13:06,940 --> 00:13:07,730
Rao Yuci,

225
00:13:09,530 --> 00:13:10,530
I know your character.

226
00:13:10,530 --> 00:13:11,850
You wouldn't resign rashly.

227
00:13:12,180 --> 00:13:13,370
As for the reason behind it,

228
00:13:14,650 --> 00:13:16,490
if you don't want to say, I won't force you.

229
00:13:18,730 --> 00:13:19,940
I'll keep this for you for now.

230
00:13:22,100 --> 00:13:23,020
(Lysen Group)

231
00:13:23,060 --> 00:13:24,100
Go and take a long vacation

232
00:13:24,100 --> 00:13:24,940
with peace of mind.

233
00:13:35,220 --> 00:13:37,010
Mr. Jiang, why don't you
take a look at this?

234
00:13:38,130 --> 00:13:39,250
I think Mr. Li

235
00:13:39,610 --> 00:13:41,060
would also be very interested.

236
00:13:50,610 --> 00:13:51,340
This is Li Qiang's

237
00:13:51,340 --> 00:13:52,490
capital flow record

238
00:13:52,490 --> 00:13:53,460
(Haoyu Shengbo)
on an offshore gambling platform.

239
00:13:54,130 --> 00:13:54,890
I traced

240
00:13:54,890 --> 00:13:56,700
the system architect of the platform,

241
00:13:57,130 --> 00:13:58,180
and by following the trail,

242
00:13:58,180 --> 00:13:59,220
I found a linked

243
00:13:59,220 --> 00:14:00,460
private bank account.

244
00:14:00,730 --> 00:14:01,490
This is the name

245
00:14:01,490 --> 00:14:02,650
of the account holder.

246
00:14:10,220 --> 00:14:13,740
(Muran Bai)

247
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:18,700
Bai Muran.

248
00:14:25,630 --> 00:14:26,580
These are the contracts

249
00:14:26,600 --> 00:14:28,010
for those green building
materials companies.

250
00:14:28,010 --> 00:14:29,010
They've all been processed.

251
00:14:29,010 --> 00:14:30,260
Review them when you have time.

252
00:14:30,730 --> 00:14:32,010
You were right about one thing.

253
00:14:32,850 --> 00:14:34,490
Bosi just announced publicly

254
00:14:34,610 --> 00:14:36,010
that their strategic direction

255
00:14:36,030 --> 00:14:37,730
has shifted
to existing housing renovation.

256
00:14:38,700 --> 00:14:39,490
Unexpectedly,

257
00:14:39,490 --> 00:14:41,340
this Beauty Pearl Society
suddenly appeared.

258
00:14:43,130 --> 00:14:45,500
Have you thought of
how to help Lysen out of this trouble?

259
00:14:46,850 --> 00:14:48,530
If it were you, what would you do?

260
00:14:52,130 --> 00:14:53,690
You've been at Lysen for so many years,

261
00:14:54,610 --> 00:14:56,940
you must have your own judgment.

262
00:14:57,730 --> 00:14:59,370
I believe you know what to do,

263
00:14:59,980 --> 00:15:01,100
even if one day

264
00:15:02,420 --> 00:15:03,610
I'm no longer at Lysen.

265
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:06,820
What do you mean, you won't be at Lysen?

266
00:15:10,650 --> 00:15:11,610
Dept 3

267
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:13,010
used to be

268
00:15:13,010 --> 00:15:14,420
the underdog in Lysen,

269
00:15:14,730 --> 00:15:15,850
but now everyone

270
00:15:15,850 --> 00:15:17,250
is in their proper place.

271
00:15:17,700 --> 00:15:19,340
And Director Ren is looking out for us.

272
00:15:20,850 --> 00:15:22,820
I am very much at ease.

273
00:15:24,420 --> 00:15:25,870
Since I'm at ease,

274
00:15:28,060 --> 00:15:29,180
I can go and settle

275
00:15:29,180 --> 00:15:30,300
some of my own affairs.

276
00:15:30,390 --> 00:15:31,530
What are you going to settle?

277
00:15:32,980 --> 00:15:33,770
Yuci.

278
00:15:37,940 --> 00:15:39,460
Didn't I say it before?

279
00:15:39,730 --> 00:15:40,700
I said very soon,

280
00:15:41,770 --> 00:15:44,420
everyone and everything
will return to their rightful owners.

281
