00:32:33,940 --> 00:32:34,730
I...

568
00:32:36,180 --> 00:32:37,770
I really wanted to adopt one.

569
00:32:38,380 --> 00:32:39,180
Later,

570
00:32:40,380 --> 00:32:42,050
someone brought over a baby.

571
00:32:44,140 --> 00:32:44,940
It was you.

572
00:32:45,860 --> 00:32:47,090
The first time I saw you,

573
00:32:47,490 --> 00:32:48,660
your little hand

574
00:32:48,980 --> 00:32:49,980
just grabbed onto me.

575
00:32:50,380 --> 00:32:51,570
At that moment, I felt

576
00:32:53,140 --> 00:32:55,090
that you were a daughter
sent to me by God.

577
00:32:55,730 --> 00:32:57,180
So I kept you.

578
00:33:00,090 --> 00:33:01,490
But who knew that six years later,

579
00:33:03,460 --> 00:33:04,730
your biological mother

580
00:33:05,660 --> 00:33:07,490
would find me with the police.

581
00:33:10,220 --> 00:33:12,490
She said you
were abducted by a neighbor.

582
00:33:13,700 --> 00:33:15,330
You had been trafficked several times.

583
00:33:16,420 --> 00:33:17,380
Come home with me.

584
00:33:17,380 --> 00:33:19,480
Your mother had also been
looking for you for six years.

585
00:33:24,460 --> 00:33:25,250
Liangliang.

586
00:33:28,180 --> 00:33:30,330
I couldn't bear to let you go back then.

587
00:33:30,620 --> 00:33:32,050
I was heartbroken, too. I...

588
00:33:32,940 --> 00:33:33,730
But you

589
00:33:34,420 --> 00:33:36,460
were someone else's child, after all.

590
00:33:40,490 --> 00:33:41,290
That's not right.

591
00:33:43,330 --> 00:33:44,140
That's not right.

592
00:33:53,460 --> 00:33:54,460
It's Rao Yuci.

593
00:33:56,330 --> 00:33:58,700
It's Rao Yuci who sent you
to say these things to me, right?

594
00:33:59,220 --> 00:34:00,380
I don't know her.

595
00:34:00,570 --> 00:34:01,940
I don't know this person.

596
00:34:02,810 --> 00:34:03,810
It's Rao Yuci.

597
00:34:04,530 --> 00:34:06,050
It's Rao Yuci and Bai Xia.

598
00:34:06,530 --> 00:34:08,420
They've teamed up against me.

599
00:34:08,490 --> 00:34:10,050
They're the ones who sent you here!

600
00:34:10,130 --> 00:34:11,210
It's Rao Yuci!

601
00:34:11,490 --> 00:34:12,740
They sent you here!

602
00:34:12,740 --> 00:34:13,460
Liangliang.

603
00:34:18,340 --> 00:34:19,420
It's Rao Yuci!

604
00:34:25,300 --> 00:34:26,090
(Bai Liangliang,)

605
00:34:27,980 --> 00:34:29,490
(I just want you to taste)

606
00:34:31,300 --> 00:34:33,340
(this kind of heart-piercing pain)

607
00:34:35,050 --> 00:34:36,690
(because you once inflicted)

608
00:34:36,690 --> 00:34:38,010
(the same pain on me.)

609
00:34:40,460 --> 00:34:42,740
(Everyone has an old dream
they'd rather not remember.)

610
00:34:43,940 --> 00:34:45,530
(But in your old dream,)

611
00:34:46,650 --> 00:34:47,980
(there lies your cruelty)

612
00:34:48,690 --> 00:34:49,650
(and your resentment.)

613
00:34:53,200 --> 00:34:54,210
(After I was discharged,)

614
00:34:54,210 --> 00:34:56,300
(I chose to start over here)

615
00:34:57,210 --> 00:34:58,610
(just for today)

616
00:35:00,050 --> 00:35:01,300
(so that here,)

617
00:35:03,210 --> 00:35:04,690
(you would have no choice but to face)

618
00:35:05,210 --> 00:35:06,980
(the karmic consequences you've hidden.)

619
00:35:27,130 --> 00:35:29,460
That knife is still here.

620
00:35:30,940 --> 00:35:31,740
It's just that

621
00:35:32,650 --> 00:35:34,420
it's not meant for you.

622
00:35:38,220 --> 00:35:41,880
=Episode 15=
(Inner Demon)

623
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:44,820
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

624
00:35:44,820 --> 00:35:51,020
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

625
00:35:51,780 --> 00:35:54,980
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

626
00:35:54,980 --> 00:35:59,500
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

627
00:35:59,500 --> 00:36:07,020
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

628
00:36:07,020 --> 00:36:10,940
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

629
00:36:10,940 --> 00:36:14,980
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

630
00:36:14,980 --> 00:36:18,500
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

631
00:36:18,500 --> 00:36:22,460
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

632
00:36:22,460 --> 00:36:26,620
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

633
00:36:26,620 --> 00:36:30,820
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

634
00:36:30,820 --> 00:36:34,620
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

635
00:36:34,620 --> 00:36:38,700
♪Keep walking through the light♪

636
00:36:38,700 --> 00:36:42,900
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

637
00:36:42,900 --> 00:36:49,220
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

638
00:37:06,340 --> 00:37:12,980
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

639
00:37:12,980 --> 00:37:16,820
♪An apology that came too late♪

640
00:37:16,820 --> 00:37:21,460
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

641
00:37:21,540 --> 00:37:28,940
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

642
00:37:28,940 --> 00:37:33,020
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

643
00:37:33,020 --> 00:37:37,100
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

644
00:37:37,100 --> 00:37:41,100
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

645
00:37:41,100 --> 00:37:44,860
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

646
00:37:44,860 --> 00:37:49,060
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

647
00:37:49,060 --> 00:37:53,220
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

648
00:37:53,220 --> 00:37:56,940
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

649
00:37:56,940 --> 00:38:00,980
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

650
00:38:00,980 --> 00:38:05,020
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

651
00:38:05,020 --> 00:38:11,220
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
